title: Female-Fronted Metal Videos (MEGAPAK)
description:
I Introduce to you a labor of love.A Collection of Female-Fronted Metal Music Videos.
They Span just about all genres from Rock,Punk,Nu-Metal,Epic,Symphonic,Death,Black and
so on.
It took me quit awhile to put this collection together.
I didn't realize how many videos I actually had.
The Quality is 720p on all videos with the exception of about 10 or 15
give or take which isn't bad considering theres 363 VIDEOS!!!!
The exception of those other few are around the 480p quality which are still decent.

All the rest are direct DVD5 and DVD9 retail disc rips!!!

I'm kinda proud of this upload and I don't expect people to
start seeding this all right away but I do ask that you do seed the videos that 
you do dload...Please..
And maybe those few die-hard fans of this genre in time could help me
SEED this ALL.

I will be seeding this upload permanently so there will always be a
chance for you to get what you want.

All my best to the fans of this genre today and forever more.

Pitufo7777
